data.description: Three Bedroom 2 bath log home on 29.6 acre cattle ranch. Fenced & crossed fenced w/ 57.42 Quonset and 30x15 barn & tack room. Four stalls with electric & water. This home has a cbs footer around the log home. New Metal Roof within the last 2 years. New a/c in 2015. Large open floor plan including a wood burning stove in the living room & 31x25 family room. Make your appointment today you will not be disappointed.By appointment only due to livestock on the property.
